			<div class="moduletable feature_area">
					<h3>Empowering and Inspiring through Challenge and Compassion</h3>
					
<div class="tab">
			Early Childhood Center	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<p>Greetings from the Early Childhood Center (ECC) section of BCIS! The ECC serves students from Toddler (2-3 years old) to Kindergarten (5-6 years old. As of the 2014-2015 year, we are based in a state-of-the-art, purpose-built facility just 1km from the main BCIS campus.<a href="/en/component/content/article/17-general/1311-early-childhood-center-toddler-to-kindergarten">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			Welcome to BCIS	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_1004.jpg" alt="DSC_1004" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/bcis-guide1_w.jpg" alt="bcis-guide1_w" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_3583.jpg" alt="DSC_3583" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_0986.jpg" alt="DSC_0986" />
<p><strong>Beijing City International School</strong> is an independent, not-for-profit, co-educational day school offering an <strong>international curriculum</strong> for <strong>Nursery to Grade 12 </strong>students. <a href="/about-us/welcome-to-bcis">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			Who We Are	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<p><img alt="535755062009122222083313464" src="/images/stories/feature_area/535755062009122222083313464.jpg" height="220" width="524" /><img alt="who" src="/images/stories/feature_area/who.jpg" height="220" width="524" /><img alt="DSC_5112cc_jpg" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_5112cc_jpg.jpg" height="220" width="524" /></p>
<p>The BCIS mission is to <strong>challenge</strong> and <strong>empower</strong> students to be <strong>compassionate</strong> and <strong>inspired</strong> people, who act for the <strong>good of all</strong> and for the <strong>sustainable development</strong> of the world. <a href="/about-us/mission-vision-a-philosophy">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			IB Curriculum	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_0350.jpg" alt="DSC_0350" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_4612.jpg" alt="DSC_4612" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_8729.jpg" alt="DSC_8729" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC4.jpg" alt="DSC4" />
<p>As an <strong>IB World School</strong>, we challenge our students to <strong>ask questions</strong>, <strong>solve problems</strong>, <strong>learn skills</strong> and <strong>be creative</strong>. Our teachers use <strong>research-based strategies</strong> to ensure outstanding student learning. <a href="/learning/curriculum">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			Experienced Faculty	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_1286.jpg" alt="DSC_1286" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_1499.jpg" alt="DSC_1499" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_3193.jpg" alt="DSC_3193" />
<p>Our dedicated teaching professionals hail from <strong>17 nationalities</strong> with an <strong>average teaching experience of 12 years</strong>. Our <strong>stringent recruitment procedures</strong> ensure that all our teachers are <strong>well-trained</strong> and possess<strong> internationally recognized professional qualifications</strong>. <a href="/community/faculty">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			Co-curricular Activities	</div>



<div class="contentpaneopen">
	<p><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSC_0041.jpg" alt="DSC_0041" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/IMG_3534.JPG" alt="IMG_3534" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/BCIS3.JPG" alt="BCIS3" /><img height="220" width="524" src="/images/stories/feature_area/DSCN1406.jpg" alt="DSCN1406" /></p>
<p>In addition to their classroom study, our students engage in <strong>a variety of inter-school sports competitions, co-curricular activities</strong> and <strong>clubs</strong> to enrich their <strong>learning experience</strong> and to develop as <strong>balanced young people</strong>. <a href="/en/learning/activities">More...</a></p>	</div>
<div class="tab">
			Professional Student Support	</div>



